      "content": "Thanks. So just to clarify, you're saying the socioeconomic stuff for Defendant B—the lack of housing and the unstable job history—would actually act more like an aggravating factor in a real courtroom? Like, instead of helping him, it makes him look like a higher risk to the court?",
